| Metric | Before | After (WebP) |
|---------|---------|----------------|
| Avg file size (photos) | 300-500KB | 50-150KB (70% reduction) |
| Load time (3G) | 2-3s | 0.5-1s |
| LCP improvement | - | 1.5-2s faster |

